            "id": "4618044",
            "title": "Bullish moves ahead with Equiniti carve-out",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Bullish (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BLSH\" title=\"Bullish\">BLSH</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20594451-bullish-announces-siris-to-acquire-non-core-equiniti-business-lines\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"said\">said</a> an affiliate of Siris has exercised its previously disclosed option to acquire three non-core Equiniti business lines—EQ Retirement Solutions, EQ Customer Resolutions and Lenvi.</li>\n<li>The carve-out will be completed alongside Bullish's planned $4.2B acquisition of Equiniti, which is expected to close in January 2027.</li>\n<li>The company also received competition law approvals for the Equiniti acquisition from the U.K., U.S. and Germany.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</body></html>",
