            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>Canadian National Railway <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20594512-cn-delivers-on-commitments-with-strong-second-quarter-results-and-raises-2026-guidance\">press release</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CNI\" title=\"Canadian National Railway Company\">CNI</a></span>): Q2 Non-GAAP EPS of C$2.08 <span> beats by C$0.12</span>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of C$4.75B (+11.2% Y/Y) <span> beats by C$130M</span>.</li>\n<li>Raised 2026 financial guidance, now assuming low single-digit RTM growth and expecting mid-to-high single-digit adjusted diluted EPS growth</li>\n<li><span>Operating ratio, defined as operating expenses as a percentage of revenues, of 62.5%, an increase of 80 basis points, and adjusted operating ratio of 62.2%, an increase of 50 basis points.</span></li>\n</ul>\n\n</body></html>",
